EE monitoring, production orders, and quality alerts.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-agen-item mex-agen-item--break">\n      <div class="mex-agen-time">12:00 – 13:00</div>\n      <div class="mex-agen-content">\n        <h3>Lunch Break</h3>\n        <p>Booth remains open for browsing.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-agen-item">\n      <div class="mex-agen-time">13:00 – 13:30</div>\n      <div class="mex-agen-content">\n        <h3>Live Demo: WMS Warehouse Operations</h3>\n        <p>sFLS warehouse management — receiving, put-away, picking, packing, and shipping with barcode scanning.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-agen-item">\n      <div class="mex-agen-time">13:30 – 14:00</div>\n      <div class="mex-agen-content">\n        <h3>Live Demo: AIoT Machine Connectivity</h3>\n        <p>Sensor data collection, real-time machine monitoring, and analytics dashboards.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-agen-item">\n      <div class="mex-agen-time">14:00 – 17:30</div>\n      <div class="mex-agen-content">\n        <h3>Open Booth — 1-on-1 Consultations Available</h3>\n        <p>Book a slot or walk up for a personalized discussion about your factory\'s specific needs.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-agen-item mex-agen-item--break">\n      <div class="mex-agen-time">17:30 – 18:00</div>\n      <div class="mex-agen-content">\n        <h3>Daily Wrap-Up</h3>\n        \n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div><!-- /wp:html -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/column -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/row -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/section -->\n<!-- wp:divi/section {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Who Should Attend"}}},"decoration":{"sizing":{"desktop":{"value":{"width":"100%","maxWidth":"none"}}},"spacing":{"desktop":{"value":{"padding":{"top":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px","right":"0px","syncVertical":"off","syncHorizontal":"off"}}}}}},"builderVersion":"5.0.0-public-beta.8","css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{background:transparent !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:divi/row {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Who Should Attend: Row"}}},"decoration":{"layout":{"desktop":{"value":{"flexWrap":"nowrap","display":"flex","flexDirection":"row","rowGap":"0px","columnGap":"0px"}}},"sizing":{"desktop":{"value":{"width":"100%","maxWidth":"none"}}},"spacing":{"desktop":{"value":{"padding":{"top":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px","right":"0px"}}}}}},"builderVersion":"5.0.0-public-beta.8","css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{max-width:100% !important;margin:0 !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:divi/column {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Who Should Attend: Column"}}},"decoration":{}},"css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{width:100% !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:html --><div class="mex-per-section">\n  <div class="mex-per-inner">\n    <span class="mex-per-label">Who This Is For</span>\n    <h2 class="mex-per-title">Is This Booth Right for You?</h2>\n    <div class="mex-per-grid">\n      \n    <div class="mex-per-card">\n      <div class="mex-per-accent"></div>\n      <div class="mex-per-body">\n        <div class="mex-per-role">Factory Owner / Operations Director</div>\n        <span class="mex-per-size">Evaluating ERP or MES</span>\n        <p class="mex-per-desc">You\'re comparing manufacturing software solutions and want to see real systems running — not just slides. You need to understand what\'s actually built for factories like yours before making a decision.</p>\n        <p class="mex-per-quote">"I want to compare solutions and see what\'s actually built for manufacturing."</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-per-card">\n      <div class="mex-per-accent"></div>\n      <div class="mex-per-body">\n        <div class="mex-per-role">ERP Implementer / Consultant</div>\n        <span class="mex-per-size">Looking for a Product Line</span>\n        <p class="mex-per-desc">You run an ERP consultancy or systems integration practice and want a manufacturing-focused product line to add to your portfolio. You need to evaluate the technology, the partner economics, and the team.</p>\n        <p class="mex-per-quote">"I\'m looking for a manufacturing-focused product line to add to my portfolio."</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div><!-- /wp:html -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/column -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/row -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/section -->\n<!-- wp:divi/section {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Proof & Social Signal"}}},"decoration":{"sizing":{"desktop":{"value":{"width":"100%","maxWidth":"none"}}},"spacing":{"desktop":{"value":{"padding":{"top":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px","right":"0px","syncVertical":"off","syncHorizontal":"off"}}}}}},"builderVersion":"5.0.0-public-beta.8","css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{background:transparent !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:divi/row {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Proof & Social Signal: Row"}}},"decoration":{"layout":{"desktop":{"value":{"flexWrap":"nowrap","display":"flex","flexDirection":"row","rowGap":"0px","columnGap":"0px"}}},"sizing":{"desktop":{"value":{"width":"100%","maxWidth":"none"}}},"spacing":{"desktop":{"value":{"padding":{"top":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px","right":"0px"}}}}}},"builderVersion":"5.0.0-public-beta.8","css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{max-width:100% !important;margin:0 !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:divi/column {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Proof & Social Signal: Column"}}},"decoration":{}},"css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{width:100% !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:html --><div class="mex-prf-section">\n  <div class="mex-prf-inner">\n    <span class="mex-prf-label">Why DigiWin Events</span>\n    <h2 class="mex-prf-title">Learn from the Team That\'s Done This 100+ Times</h2>\n    <div class="mex-prf-stats-bar">\n      \n    <div class="mex-prf-stat">\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-value">100+</div>\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-label">Thai Implementations</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-prf-stat">\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-value">44</div>\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-label">Years Manufacturing ERP</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-prf-stat">\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-value">95%</div>\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-label">Contract Renewal Rate</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class="mex-prf-stat">\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-value">50+</div>\n      <div class="mex-prf-stat-label">Thai Team Members</div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class="mex-prf-text">DigiWin has been serving Thai manufacturers for 8 years with ERP, MES, WMS, and AIoT solutions purpose-built for the factory floor. At our booth, you\'ll meet the same consultants who implement these systems — not salespeople reading from scripts.</p>\n  </div>\n</div><!-- /wp:html -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/column -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/row -->\n<!-- /wp:divi/section -->\n<!-- wp:divi/section {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Logistics"}}},"decoration":{"sizing":{"desktop":{"value":{"width":"100%","maxWidth":"none"}}},"spacing":{"desktop":{"value":{"padding":{"top":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px","right":"0px","syncVertical":"off","syncHorizontal":"off"}}}}}},"builderVersion":"5.0.0-public-beta.8","css":{"desktop":{"value":{"freeForm":"selector{background:transparent !important;padding:0 !important;}"}}}} -->\n<!-- wp:divi/row {"module":{"meta":{"adminLabel":{"desktop":{"value":"Logistics: Row"}}},"decoration":{"layout":{"desktop":{"value":{"flexWrap":"nowrap","display":"flex","flexDirection":"row","rowGap":"0px","columnGap":"0px"}}},"sizing":{"desktop":{"value":{"width":"100%","maxWidth":"none"}}},"spacing":{"desktop":{"value":{"padding":{"top":"0px","bottom":"0px","left":"0px","right":"0px"}}}}}},"builderVersion":"5.0.